DestroyModuleConfig FvwmBacker: *

# first set a default background
*FvwmBacker: Command (Desk *, Page * *) \
	Exec xpmroot $FT_DATADIR/themes/awol/images/background/bckgnd3.xpm
*FvwmBacker: Command (Desk *, Page * 0) \
	Exec xpmroot $FT_DATADIR/themes/awol/images/background/bckgnd3.xpm
*FvwmBacker: Command (Desk *, Page * 1) \
	Exec xpmroot $FT_DATADIR/themes/awol/images/background/bckgnd1.xpm
*FvwmBacker: Command (Desk *, Page * 2) \
	Exec xpmroot $FT_DATADIR/themes/awol/images/background/bckgnd3.xpm
*FvwmBacker: Command (Desk *, Page * 3) \
	Exec xpmroot $FT_DATADIR/themes/awol/images/background/bckgnd1.xpm

DestroyFunc FuncFvwmStartThemeBackground
AddToFunc   FuncFvwmStartThemeBackground
+ I FuncFvwmRestartModule FvwmBacker

DestroyFunc FuncFvwmStopThemeBackground
AddToFunc   FuncFvwmStopThemeBackground
+ I FuncFvwmStopModule FvwmBacker
